This change updates the `getOutputDirName` method to handle this.

pull_request.title: Collect lockfileVersion for yarn
pull_request.body: This PR gets the lockfile version from a `yarn.lock` into the returned value from `scanParentDirs`. This function is used by the Vercel build container for DD tracing, and we are currently missing the lockfileVersion when the package manager is yarn.

pull_request.title: [tests] Add package-lock.json file to dev-server-and-routes vc dev fixture
pull_request.body: This fixture sometimes fails with `Error: Command failed with exit code 1: yarn install at makeError`. We've noticed that a common theme among flakey tests is errors with yarn. This adds a `package-lock.json` file to switch this over to use `npm`.
